node.text:
It was the hardest stage of the season so far in @mxgp as @romainfebvre took the overall win in Lommel! 

@jeffrey_herlings84 was the hero of the weekend by coming back from injury to take P2 overall and a race win. 

It was an all Astars MX podium as @paulsjonass41 took his first podium of the season finishing P3! 

In MX2 @jagogeerts93 took the overall win, and in Women’s MX it was @shanavdvlist188 that finished in first position. 

#AlpinestarsMX #RacingAhead #Alpinestars #Tech10 #SM10 #AlpinestarsHelmets #AlpinestarsWomens

node.text:
The Alpinestars SM5 Helmet. 🙌 

Astars Quick Facts:

We scrutinized every possible aspect to engineer a helmet that is safe and thoughtfully designed to deliver optimal protection and comfort.

The SM5 was engineered with a raised area with padding to effectively reduce the forces transmitted to the collarbone and a patented visor release system that ensures the visor is released with the correct pre-determined amount of force, irrespective of the angle of impact.

Starting Price: $239.95

#ThinkingAhead #SM5Helmet #AlpinestarsHelmets
